  • Constructor Details

    • Adult

      public Adult​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String birthday, java.lang.String ssn, float income, java.lang.String employer)
      This initializes a new Adult Instance, setting its name, birthday, ssn, income, and employer.
      Parameters:
      name - Adult's name (non-digit)
      birthday - Represents birthday of adult, although must follow format of xxxx/xx/xx (year, month, day), where x are numeric.
      ssn - Represents the social security number of an adult, although must follow format of xxx-xx-xxxx, where x are numerical values.
      income - Represents a gross income/wage of an Adult (must be non-negative).
      employer - Represents the employer of the given Adult.
